data.description: Welcome to this charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home located in the desirable community of Martinez, just outside Augusta. Step inside to discover the allure of laminate wood floors, providing both style and durability throughout the living spaces. Gather around the fireplace in the living room, creating a cozy focal point that adds warmth and character to the heart of the home. Experience the luxury of spacious bedrooms, offering a retreat for relaxation and personalization for every member of the household. Enjoy the convenience of nearby restaurants and shopping, making daily errands and dining out a delightful experience. Explore the vibrant culture of Downtown Augusta, just a short 15-minute drive away, offering a mix of entertainment, dining, and cultural attractions. Embrace the outdoors with a potential for outdoor living spaces, providing opportunities for gardening, entertaining, or simply enjoying the fresh air. With its combination of location, features, and modern comforts, this home is move-in ready, inviting you to start the next chapter of your life. Martinez offers the perfect balance of suburban tranquility and proximity to the excitement of Augusta, creating an ideal setting for a fulfilling lifestyle. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this Martinez residence your new home - where comfort, style, and convenience converge seamlessly! Roof is less than 4 years old HVAC is 3-5 years old Water Heater is 1.5 years old
